This is a map I made as a work in progress a while back. While certainly not perfect, I couldn't get access to more assets to make forest look more like.. well, a forest. So this'll do. It's got basic lighting and the map layout is balanced. 

- Still need to make minimap, otherwise finished. (EDIT: I think the minimap works now but I haven't tested it)

****UPDATE:**** I noticed that alot of people were commenting on a lack of ambient sound, I just checked and I forgot to include my custom soudscape and soundfiles!! I have just updated the ZIP file to include these files, simply redownload and re-extract to your CS folder (not your maps folder! Hello everyone, Im pleased to announce the release of De_Forest! There's been alot of blood sweat and tears to get this into the state it is today, also figuring out how the hell to make a forest map work in the Source engine, but Im pretty proud of how it looks and plays now. It should run well on most systems with a ati 9800 / nvidia 6xxx or above, not sure about below that as I havent been able to test on lower end systems. Intro: ======= Terrorists have been hiding out in the woods for months and are being hunted down for information on spies within a number of high ranking organisations assisting in plotting terror attacks. As the terrorist team you must destroy all evidence of such activities by planting bombs at either of the two sites which were being used as the hideout. As the CTs you must secure the hideouts and prevent the terrorists from destorying the information. Tips: ====== If you get lost, find your way back to the river and look for landmarks which will point you in the right direction. There are also many signposts dotted around the forest to help you find your way to the bombsites. Footnote: ========= Thanks to everyone who offered feedback and advice on this map, its been a big challenge and a hard journey and I hope you have fun!

De_foodcourt - Bomb-Defuse
By Amstrad (hated.proud at gmail dot com)

A group of fanatical Terrorists has taken control of Oak Lake Galleria and are now intent on detonating a package of C4 explosives at it's heart. A hastily assembled Counter-Terrorism unit has been dispatched to the scene.

Terrorists: Eliminate all opposition and plant the C4 explosives at the foodcourt's center.

Counter-Terrorists: Prevent the Terrorists from succesfully detonating their package.

-------------------------------------------------

This will be my first map completed to a great enough degree that I feel it release worthy. As such I've taken my time to make sure it has a touch of polish before I kicked it out the door. Map includes custom textures as well as the overview and radar maps. The bot nav-file was not tuned but appears to be balanced after some observation.

I'm sure I missed something or screwed up somewhere.
Comments, suggestions for improvement or flames (if you feel it necessary) are all welcome at my email.
Send mail at info@backsoftware.com for more information

STORY:
A local over-the-counter pharmacy company called Nevrin Inc. has stolen some biochemical matereals from a warehouse belonging to a not-so-over-the-counter underground import business (Handling everything from drugs to guns to depleted uranium). After the mafia caught on to this, they began threatening Nevrin Inc. which called for support from law enforcement only to notice much to it's dismay that the only tunnel connecting them by road to the rest of the city was scheduled for a renovation. The Mafia took this as an oppertunity to send in some goons it hired as mercenaries to teach Nevrin a lesson, with some good ol' C4. The mercenaries are by no means aware that the police are already on the scene via a tug they "borrowed" from another local company.

Hilarity insues.

T Objectives:
A:Blow up the Nevrin factory. Who cares if our matereals will go with it? NO ONE FUCKS WITH DA MOB.
B:Eliminate any and all resistance in the area that they hired to protect them because NO ONE FUCKS WITH DA MOB.
C:Blow up the tug that police borrowed because we need to show them THAT NO ONE FUCKS WITH DA MOB.

CT objectives:
A:Stop the factory from being blown up.
B:Stop the tug from being sunk, we don't have the budget to pay for the damages unless we go back to using YUGOs for patrolling *gasp*.
C:eliminate any mercenaries/thugs/mafiosi/terrorists in the area. Be sure to shoot first and ask questions later.

There are also a few weapons lying around the map mostly in or near the where the CTs set up an improvised base of operations and the Mafia's little warehouse. The exception is a pair of shotguns and a few grenades in a van that broke down on the overpass.

Hello, this is my map that I made for the clan I am apart of. It is rather small, and from what I think now, shouldn't be a DE map. Personally, I think AIM would suit it better.

Anyway, I first started by making it a Dev textured map at the start, but many people told me it made the mapper look lazy, so I did a quick texture job. It isn't amazing, but It made the map look much better (from what my testers say). I think it looks much like a paintball arena.

Bomb zone B is furthest to the southeast corner, and opposite for A.

The map was intended for around 6v6.

If you have any questions, ask. If you have any critique, please state it. I realize that there are very minor mistakes in the geometry and texture, but its nothing that will disrupt game play or distract players.

If you ever want to drop by me and my friends clan server, the IP is 69.12.100.136:27015.

You can decompile my map if you wish but please ask for my permission first and make sure to just throw my name in the credits.

High-quality port for CS:S of the Release Candidate 1 of remarkable samenamed midsize map from CS:GO by Mr. Mcsnoogies.
This port contains some constructive and visual changes in comparison with the original, which was made for bigger detailing and improvement of the gameplay smoothness.

Story:
   Fend Hospital & Medical Center, located in Washington State near Mt. St. Helens, has been taken over by a organized criminal group.
   The bandits must destroy the evidence of their wrongdoings before it can be seized by the enforcement service.
   The task force need to prevent the implementation of these plans...

Fedra is a nice little village set in the mountains. The counterterroists' spawn is around and in a small house that is near bombspot A and a stretch away from B. The terrorists spawn point is on the other end of the village, equidistant to A and B. This is an extended version with changes such as: -models from the game S.T.A.L.K.E.R. -custom textures -A tunnelsystem -new ways to A and B -An elevator at bombspot A -more houses you can enter. There are: - 64 Player-spawns - 2 Bombspots - radar map in bsp - soundscapes - 3d skybox with moving clouds - use of hint/ skip texture and areaportals render-time: 1 min 58 sec Optimized, balanced and tested with and for 64 Players on the Sachsenkneipe servers. Special thanks to www.sachsenkneipe.de for testing and improving it!
